What is it?
=============================

![image](https://oer.gitlab.io/oer-on-oer-infrastructure/figures/OS/containers.png)

Advantages
=============================

* Efficient
* Portability
* Reproducibility
* Automated

Disadvantages:
=============================
* Persistent Data Storage
* GUI
* Speed (if required)

